<bibRefCitation author="Rehn" box="[375,508,367,393]" pageId="1" pageNumber="36" refString="Rehn, J. A. G. (1945) A new genus and species of Phaneropterinae from eastern Peru. Notulae Naturae, 150, 1 - 7." type="journal article" year="1945">
